   Braga Calandrini De Azevedo, Celia M. and Gerold, Gerhard},
Title = {DEGRADED PASTURE DISTRIBUTION AND WOODY ENRICHMENT STRATEGIES FOR
   PASTURE FERTILITY PRESERVATION IN THE BRAGANTINA REGION, NORTH-EASTERN
   AMAZON},
