   current status of industrial agriculture along with lessons learned from
   industrialized agricultural production patterns, industrialized
   agricultural production processes, and the industrialized agri-food
   supply chain. Furthermore, five emerging technologies, namely the
   Internet of Things, robotics, artificial intelligence, big data
   analytics, and blockchain, toward Agriculture 4.0 are discussed.
